# Commit messages

- Imperative mood, 1–2 sentences, focus on **why**.
- Good: `Fix intake prefill when Gemini is unavailable.`
- Avoid: `updated files`, `WIP`, `fix bug`

Match recent repo style (`Add …`, `Fix …`). Squash merge PR title can match the commit message.
